---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
import PageHero from "../components/PageHero.astro";
import { business } from "../data/site";
---
<Base
  title="Cookie Policy"
  description="How Angel Plumbing Services Ltd uses cookies and local storage on this website, and how you can control them."
  path="/cookie-policy"
>
  <PageHero eyebrow="Legal" title="Cookie Policy"
    crumbs={[{ label: "Home", href: "/" }, { label: "Cookie Policy", href: "/cookie-policy" }]} />

  <section class="bg-cream">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[80rem] px-4 sm:px-6 py-16 sm:py-20">
      <div class="prose-legal">
        <p>This Cookie Policy explains how {business.legalName} uses cookies and similar technologies on
          this website. We keep our use of cookies to a minimum.</p>

        <h2>What are cookies?</h2>
        <p>Cookies are small text files placed on your device when you visit a website. Similar
          technologies, such as local storage, let a site remember information in your browser. They can
          be "essential" (needed for the site to work) or "optional" (for example analytics).</p>

        <h2>Cookies we use</h2>
        <h3>Essential</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>We store your cookie choice (accept or reject) in your browser's local storage so we don't
            ask you on every visit. This is essential and is set regardless of your choice.</li>
          <li>Our on-site tools (the period-property tool and CP12 reminder tool) may save your progress
            in your browser's local storage so you don't lose your place. This data stays on your device.</li>
        </ul>
        <h3>Optional - analytics</h3>
        <p>We would like to set optional analytics cookies to understand how visitors use the site so we
          can improve it. These are only set if you select "Accept all" in our cookie banner. If you
          select "Reject optional", no analytics cookies are set.</p>

        <h2>Managing your choice</h2>
        <p>You can change your mind at any time by clearing this site's data in your browser, which will
          remove your stored choice and show the cookie banner again. You can also block or delete cookies
          through your browser settings. Blocking essential storage may affect how the site works.</p>

        <h2>More information</h2>
        <p>For more on how we handle personal data, see our <a href="/privacy-policy">Privacy Policy</a>.
          For general guidance on cookies you can visit the ICO at
          <a href="https://ico.org.uk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">ico.org.uk</a>. Questions? Email
          <a href={`mailto:${business.email}`}>{business.email}</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
